description: Application for reserved matters (scale, layout, appearance, access landscaping, planting, and access) and the construction of 216 residential units (118 market, 97 intermediate and 1 social rented unit), including parking and new landscaped public space for Phase 5 (Block A, B, C and G) pursuant to conditions 5 and 6 following approval of hybrid planning application H/01054/13 dated 20/11/2013.
